ur personal network • Activate dormant relationships with a substantive reason to reconnect • Help clients understand the real numbers, real timelines, and real risks — so they can make an informed decision • Walk alongside clients from first conversation through to permit in hand • Build trust through genuine conversation — not scripts or pressure tactics • Work remotely with full support from our Athens headquarters\nWe are not looking for cold-callers, lead-chasers, or people hoping to build a network from scratch on the job. We are looking for trusted connectors who already have one.\nWho Our Clients Are\n• Entrepreneurs, business owners, and investors with €250,000–€800,000+ to invest • Self-made successes who built wealth through talent and persistence • Often from environments where institutions have failed them — they are sceptical for good reason • Looking for optionality: security, Schengen access, European education, and peace of mind for their families • They value relationships over transactions and will not be rushed or pressured\nOur clients need someone who already understands their world, respects their scepticism, and guides with patience and honesty.\nWhat We're Looking For\nEssential:• An established personal network of high-net-worth individuals you can credibly introduce to a serious opportunity — this is non-negotiable • Cultural fluency — you genuinely belong to the communities you would serve, not just market to them • Fluent English (written and verbal) • Comfortable with commission-only compensation • Integrity — you would rather lose a deal than mislead someone in your network\nHighly Desirable:• Experience in real estate, immigration, wealth management, or financial servicesBackgrounds that often do well:• Business owners and entrepreneurs with peer networks of fellow founders • Private bankers and wealth managers with a client book they can speak to independently • Lawyers and accountants serving affluent clients • Real estate professionals active in investment or luxury markets • Community leaders and well-connected professionals with genuine standing in diaspora or HNW communities\nWhat You Get• Access to training and information about our programmes — no cost to you • Conversation guides designed for high-stakes, trust-based advisory — not generic sales scripts • CRM system for pipeline management • Branded marketing materials ready to share with your contacts • Direct support from our Athens headquarters — legal coordination, transaction management, and immigration filing handled for you • As we grow together, you will receive warm leads from our marketing campaigns alongside your own network"}
