{"source":"linkedin","source_id":"4409011248","title":"Head of Business Development","company":"OneBullEx","location":"Dubai, Dubai, United Arab Emirates","remote":true,"salary":"","posted_at":"","url":"https://grnh.se/gv1hraf2teu","description":"OneBullEx is a next-generation, AI-native derivatives trading platform designed to bridge the gap between enterprise-grade quantitative research and exchange-level execution.\n\nOur ecosystem features OneALPHA, a natural-language quantitative research pipeline, and 300 SPARTANS, a systematic execution layer that automates high-performance strategies. By embedding AI-driven validation and \"glass-box\" transparency directly into our exchange infrastructure, OneBullEx is redefining operational integrity and trading efficiency for the crypto derivatives era.\n\nThe Mission\n\nAs the Head of Business Development, you will be the chief architect of OneBullEx's market growth and the commander of our global commercial engine. We are seeking a battle-tested executive from a top-tier Centralised Exchange who possesses a deep technical understanding of the futures market and the leadership gravity to command a high-performing, global team. You will own the full BD lifecycle—from setting aggressive KPIs and professional client onboarding to managing the operational workflows that keep our liquidity deep and our ecosystem thriving.\n\nCore Responsibilities\n\nStrategic Growth: Design and execute a global roadmap to scale derivatives volume, specifically focusing on perpetual swaps and professional market share. Operational Leadership: Direct the entire BD department, establishing high-standard KPIs, optimising CRM pipelines (HubSpot/Salesforce), and perfecting the \"lead-to-trade\" funnel. Liquidity & Market Maker Relations: Sourcing and managing partnerships with Tier-1 Market Makers (MMs) and HFT firms to maintain superior order book depth. Product Synergy: Bridge the gap between Business Development and Product/Quant teams to align 