{"source":"linkedin","source_id":"4405555520","title":"HNW Network Connector - Saudi & GCC","company":"PassBeyond","location":"Athens","remote":true,"salary":"","posted_at":"","url":"https://sa.linkedin.com/jobs/view/hnw-network-connector-saudi-gcc-at-passbeyond-4405555520?position=8&pageNum=0&refId=mx%2FsL6mZvEUCpV30zWu6zA%3D%3D&trackingId=x5RYsPEfcbKi64cNZ7wtCQ%3D%3D","description":"📍 Remote | Report to Athens HQ 💼 Independent Contractor 💰 Uncapped commission — top performers earn €200,000+\nWho We Are\nWe believe ambitious people should not be prisoners of their passport.PassBeyond helps high-net-worth individuals secure European residency and citizenship through Greek property investment. Our clients invest €250,000–€800,000+ and receive residency or citizenship for themselves and their families — gaining Schengen access, euro-denominated assets, and long-term optionality.\nFounded by Andreas Afeldt, based full-time in Athens, who has spent over a decade working with high-net-worth clients across international markets. PassBeyond sits between global institutional scale and personal, founder-led trust — with deep local knowledge in Greece and cultural fluency across every market we serve.\nThe Role: Bring Your Network. We Bring Everything Else.\nThis is not a traditional sales role, and we are not building a call centre. We are looking exclusively for individuals who have already spent years — sometimes decades — building a personal network of high-net-worth entrepreneurs, business owners, investors, and senior professionals.\nYour network is the asset. Our job is to make it more valuable.\nIf you already move in the right circles, we give you a credible, high-value opportunity to introduce to the people who already trust you — backed by a full operational engine in Athens that handles legal, transactional, and immigration work for you.\nYou will:• Introduce PassBeyond to high-net-worth individuals already in your personal network • Activate dormant relationships