ity leaders and well-connected professionals with genuine standing in diaspora or HNW communities\nWhat You Get• Access to training and information about our programmes — no cost to you • Conversation guides designed for high-stakes, trust-based advisory — not generic sales scripts • CRM system for pipeline management • Branded marketing materials ready to share with your contacts • Direct support from our Athens headquarters — legal coordination, transaction management, and immigration filing handled for you • As we grow together, you will receive warm leads from our marketing campaigns alongside your own network"}
