ule discovery calls and product discussions for senior sales managers\n* Maintain accurate prospect and opportunity data in Salesforce CRM\n* Learn and follow a structured sales process and methodology (training provided)\n* Collaborate with marketing and pre-sales teams to support campaigns and proposals\n* Drive sales deals in your region\n* Meet defined monthly and quarterly activity and pipeline targets\n\n*Qualifications*\n\n* Bachelor’s degree in business, Marketing, Technology, or a related field with 3.5+ GPA\n* Minimum 4 years to Maximum 8 years of experience in SaaS sales , Technology sales\n* Candidates strong communication and learning ability are welcome to apply\n* The candidate should have a prior experience in SaaS sales, Technology Sales otherwise resume should be rejected in the screening\n\n*Skills & Competencies*\n\n* Strong verbal and written communication skills\n* Comfortable with outbound outreach and customer conversations\n* Experience technology, telecom, SaaS, and AI-driven solutions\n* Basic understanding (or strong interest) in B2B sales and consultative selling\n* Ability to learn CRM tools (Salesforce experience is a plus, not mandatory)\n* Organized, persistent, and results-oriented mindset\n* Willingness to learn structured sales frameworks and best practices\n\n*What You’ll Learn & Gain*\n\n* Hands-on exposure to enterprise SaaS and telecom solution selling\n* Training on BSS, network applications, and GenAI-powered platforms\n* Experience working with European telecom operators and partners\n* Clear growth path into Senior Sales roles\n* Mentorship from experienced sales leaders in a global environment\n\nPay: AED220,350.00 - AED250,000.00 per year\n\nWork Location: Remote"}
